name: Virtual Phenomenology 33
description:
"You Know, I Was Afraid At First, But Now I'm Ready. No Matter Where I Go Or What I See, I Know I Can Always Come Back Here." 

Field note recording taken whilst conducting ethnographic research in a virtual world. Paopu fruit trees waving in the breeze recorded on the Destiny Islands in Kingdom Hearts. According to legend, "If two people share one, their destinies become intertwined. They'll remain a part of each other's lives no matter what." Here's to a new chapter HENnies. DM for file download.
